# text = Supper was comfortably served and hot, though my aunt’s rooms were very high up--whether that she might have more stone stairs for her money, or might be nearer to the door in the roof, I don’t know--and consisted of a roast fowl, a steak, and some vegetables, to all of which I did ample justice, and which were all excellent.
